# Optional local overrides — copy to .env (never commit .env).
#
# Firestore rules tests (npm run test:rules):
#   No credentials needed. Uses the local Firestore emulator only.
#   Requires Java 21+ on PATH (see README Prerequisites).
#
# Optional — only if you add App Check or other server-side tooling later:
# FIREBASE_APPCHECK_SITE_KEY=
# GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=path/to/serviceAccount.json
